  "title": "A bright star-like UFO was sighted hovering over Brasília-DF [1996]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/29/a-bright-star-like-ufo-was-sighted-hovering-over-brasilia-df-1996/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1ev",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>MARCH 21st, 1996</strong>. Time: 19h51. Duration: 30 minutes. In the Plano Piloto region, in Brasília, Distrito Federal, two people followed the trajectory of an unidentified flying object in the form of &#8220;a star &#8211; but brighter&#8221; and  with a size &#8220;larger than a star&#8221;. According to the witness who reported the sighting, the UFO was at the &#8220;airplanes&#8221; altitude, but &#8220;stationary&#8221; amidst few clouds in a clear sky. It was also reported that the UFO moved &#8220;from the Pilot Plan to Guará&#8221; in the Distrito Federal.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.421. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre a ocorrência de objeto voador na região do Plano Piloto, Brasília, Distrito Federal”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n",
